snippet.title: Sierra Ops - Episode 2 Release Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
"Woefully ill-prepared, play as Captain Fahrenheit as they uncover long-lost secrets new and old, while fighting in an impossible war between Earth and Mars." 
🌘Play Sierra Ops here : https://store.steampowered.com/app/364210

Follow us on Twitter for updates : https://twitter.com/sierralunabot
or join our Discord server : https://discord.gg/TRuCZZXuwc

Support us on Patreon! https://www.patreon.com/InnoMen

Voice Actors:
Narration by Elise-Meggie

Main Characters:
Junius Fahrenheit - Christopher Escalante
Allen Fallauro - Eli Farmer
Freija Tal - Tina Kim
Jean Brookes - Anairis Quiñones
Claine de Lune - Sydney Poniewaz
Almon Rutherford - Connor Marc Colquhoun
Ares Dreadnought Captain - Kevin Liberty
Ares Admiral - Patrick M. Seymour

Game Staff:
Tooaya - character design and CG artwork
Shawnee "Youko" Liu - writer/director
Glean "Kemeo" Yap - programmer/game design
Jester "Jezer0" Go - Video/UI/Animations/QA
Tobby "Msrsgtshooterperson" Ong - Backgrounds/2D/3D CG
Arvin "Colin Tremingway" Cua - Music composition
Jason "Helrouis" Cheng - management/game design/QA
